# language:en
Feature: Monitoring redis service

  Scenario: Monitoring
    Given that recipe "redis" is run
    Then service "redis_service" should be running
    And the condition "this service should be accessible over tcp" should hold
    And this condition should be monitored 

    And the condition "anonymous user should be able to log into this service" should hold
    And this condition should be monitored by "redis_basic_health"
      When the value of attribute "sap" is available
